I would like to remove myself entirely from the decision process

14
00:00:44,919 --> 00:00:48,903
给自己一个永久的假期 让自己一辈子都不做仁慈的独裁者
by giving myself a permanent vacation from being benevolent dictator for life.

15
00:00:50,450 --> 00:00:52,348
你们都要靠自己了
You will all be on your own.

16
00:00:52,668 --> 00:00:55,432
