Or, in our open source world, were languages more like spoken languages,

30
00:01:39,151 --> 00:01:41,200
取决于所有语言使用者的行为？
things that grow and react

31
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:44,586
取决于所有语言使用者的行为？
according to the behavior of a whole bunch of different speakers?

32
00:01:45,482 --> 00:01:50,080
Python 社区 这个成长速度远超其他语言的社区
The Python community, the fastest growing community of any language out there

33
00:01:50,336 --> 00:01:51,606
很快就会找到这个问题的答案
was about to find out.

34
