I think one of the reasons why Python has become such a diverse community

139
00:08:49,912 --> 00:08:51,446
原因之一就是吉多本人
is because of Guido.

140
00:08:51,766 --> 00:08:55,050
Python 现在能够拥有女性核心开发者
Python has female core developers now

141
00:08:55,434 --> 00:09:00,826
